      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is, ideally for someone looking for a project or a parts car. The exterior has significant paint failure, heavy rusting on the rocker panels, and several large dents. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a noticeable knock, the transmission shifts harshly, and the suspension requires a complete overhaul. The interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics; it will need a dedicated owner to return it to a roadworthy state.",
