    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen has undergone a comprehensive mechanical validation, including a documented VANOS system overhaul and structural subframe reinforcement to ensure peak torsional rigidity. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox offers precise, tactile shifts, feeding power through a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential. The chassis remains in showroom configuration with original bushings and a pristine undercarriage. Every factory tolerance is met, and the Nappa leather interior shows zero bolster wear, reflecting a vehicle that has been maintained with clinical precision.",
